From a3a933072559fd6f53382c6bdad52a761f5883a1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Bartek=20Iwa=C5=84czuk?= <biwanczuk@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 18:14:56 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] perf(ext/node): convert more polyfills to lazy-loaded JS

Converts 7 internal Node.js polyfill modules from eagerly-loaded ESM to
lazy-loaded JS (IIFE pattern), reducing startup overhead when these
modules aren't needed:

- internal_binding/_timingSafeEqual.ts
- internal_binding/crypto.ts
- internal_binding/cares_wrap.ts
- internal_binding/http_parser.ts
- internal/tls_common.js
- internal/streams/add-abort-signal.js
- internal/crypto/util.ts
